{
  "stem": "1753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, finally, later on that year, was late in 1940 when they closed the Lodz ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, things started to get tough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and I have to tell you, you know, in-- in-- in rooms that would normally be, maybe, good for-- for two-- for two individuals, as many as six, eight people lived in that room.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we were assigned a room with a-- with another Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were-- there were four of them, and two of us, so six people in one room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the bedroom, the living room, the kitchen, and you name it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I was an enterprising individual, so I got myself-- I learned of some factory in the ghetto that was packaging spices, puddings, and baking powders, cinnamon, and pepper, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I got a job with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I smuggled myself out every day, out of the ghetto, and sold that stuff on the--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the Christian side.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you had to-- had to pay somebody to smuggle yourself out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to pay somebody to smuggle yourself in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, when you-- you take off your your-- your-- armband, which--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews and Pollacks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All depends where the business going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was no major-- that was just a little fee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I did good business, and I supported my father that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was risky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in fact, a few times, I almost got myself in real deep, deep trouble, but I somehow got out of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That would be in December, 1940, and early January, February, 1941.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day, I heard of about-- of a camp outside Warsaw where they treat people fairly well.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
